3 pounds ground beef
3 big pinches of salt
3 pinches of pepper
sleeve of saltines crunched real good
2ish eggs (double the recipe, just add one more egg)
half an onion, minced and caramelized
barbecue sauce (don't go crazy but don't be stingy)

mix it all together really well
make it loaf shaped (if doubling, make 2 loafs)
air fryer pan
smoke at 250 for maybe 4 hours
Baste with bbq the last hour

